videos.description: Ebuka Izundu is strong on the offensive boards to create a 3-point play on a putback.
videos.headline: Miami's Izundu makes 3-point play on putback

videos.description: BC's Jordan Chatman forces a turnover and looks up to Ky Bowman for the one-handed slam.
videos.headline: Chatman sets up Bowman for throwdown

videos.description: BC's Jerome Robinson sinks the jumper and is fouled for a potential 3-point play.
videos.headline: Robinson pulls up for bucket

videos.description: BC's Jerome Robinson powers to the hoop and sinks the circus shot on a lay-in.
videos.headline: Robinson makes circus shot with two defenders on him

videos.description: BC's Steffon Mitchell denies Lonnie Walker IV which leads to Ky Bowman being fouled on the ensuing breakaway.
videos.headline: Mitchell's crucial block helps tie game
